replies.body:
How were Taliyah and Ekko a waste of potential?
You can go multiple builds on Ekko at ease, and he's just fine the way he is now.

Taliyah is at a person's skill discretion. You can either do nothing with her, or do anything you want. But are you going to tell me that all of these are wrong? Cause if so, continue to tell a level 7 of both that he's wrong {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-popcorn}}
